"Let's Create! Pottery 2" Application Privacy Policy
At Infinite Dreams, we care about your data. Please take a while and have a look at our privacy policy and understand what kind of data we collect and why we do it. "Let's Create! Pottery 2" is a mobile application where users can create, share, comment and rate unique images of pottery designs. In order to provide this service to you, we need to collect, store, and process some of your personal data.
WHY WE COLLECT DATA?
There are several reasons why we do that:
To enable posting pottery images in "Let's Create! Pottery 2" application.
To store your game progress securely in the cloud.
To improve the overall experience by analyzing statistical, non-personalized data about events in the game.
FACEBOOK LOGIN
In "Let's Create! Pottery 2" application, you can post your pottery images. The image can be viewed, rated, and commented by other players. Please note that any pottery image, rating, or comment that you provide to us is information you are asking us to make public. Once you create an account in the application, we will collect, store, and process some personal information in our database. The data that we collect, store, and process may include:
Pottery images, comments, votes, and other information for the voting system.
CLOUD STORAGE
In order to securely store your game progress, once you sign in to Game Center (iOS) or Google Play Games (Android), we store and process some of your personal data:
Gamer ID (Android).
Game Center ID (iOS).
ANALYTICS
"Let's Create! Pottery" use analytics (usage data) to understand how users engage with the game and how to improve the overall experience. The information gathered includes the device type, the session length, interactions with various user interface elements in the game. We do not store this data on our servers but pass it to our partners. Our partners have their privacy policies. Please visit their websites to find more information. The analytics partners that we work with are:
Google Analytics:
https://www.google.com/analytics
Unity Analytics:
https://unity.com/solutions/analytics
Data that we collect and provide to our partners for analytics may include:
Unique device and user identifiers.
Anonymized IP address.
AGE LIMITS
We do believe, "Let's Create! Pottery 2" is a safe and kids friendly game. However, due to the social element of the game and the ability to share pottery images with the community, we do not allow minors under 13 years old to create the accounts. We do not knowingly collect or solicit personal data about or direct or target interest-based advertising to anyone under the age of 13 or knowingly allow such persons to use our Services. No one under the age of 13 may provide any personal data. If we learn that we have collected personal data about a child under age 13, we will delete that data as quickly as possible. If you believe that we might have any data from or about a child under the age of 13, please contact us.
HOW TO GET YOUR DATA REMOVED
If you'd like to get all of your data removed, please contact us at support@idreams.pl
CHANGES TO THIS PRIVACY STATEMENT
Infinite Dreams may amend this Privacy Statement from time to time. Use of information we collect now is subject to the Privacy Statement in effect at the time such information is used.
OWNER, DATA CONTROLLER AND DATA PROCESSOR
Address: Infinite Dreams sp. z o.o., ul. Bojkowska 45, 44-100 Gliwice, Poland
